{{Infobox award | name = Kultainen Venla | image = | alt = | caption = | description = Excellence in Television | presenter = [[Televisioakatemia]] | country = Finland | year = 2010 | website = http://www.kultainenvenla.fi }}
The Finnish Television Academy ([[Televisioakatemia|Televisioakatemia RY]]) organizes the '''Golden Venla''' ('''Kultainen Venla''') competition and gala. The Golden Venla Awards recognize the year's best Finnish television programs, their creators and performers.<ref>{{cite web|title=Association of independent producers in Finland (SATU ry)|url=http://satu.fi/english|website=http://satu.fi/english}}</ref> The Golden Venlas are voted on by members of the Academy - professionals working in the industry.<ref>{{cite web|title=Kultainen Venla website|url=http://kultainenvenla.fi/etusivu/|website=kultainenvenla.fi}}</ref>
